[29/01/2019 04:00:29] <font color="#ffffff">-Hasta luego.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:00:29] <font color="#ffffff">-Agur.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:00:30] <font color="#ffffff">-Vamos a conocer a Álex ChiCón,</font>
