[29/01/2019 04:11:12] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Anda!</font>
[29/01/2019 04:11:14] <font color="#ffffff">-Arigato.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:11:16] <font color="#ffffff">-¿Sois solidarios los vascos?</font>
