[29/01/2019 04:45:02] <font color="#ffffff">-Venga.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:45:03] <font color="#ffffff">-Hello.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:45:03] <font color="#ffffff">-Hello.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:45:05] <font color="#ffffff">-Good afternoon.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:45:05] <font color="#ffffff">-Good afternoon.</font>
[29/01/2019 04:45:08] <font color="#ffffff">-En Alemania,</font>
